author: thomreis
body:
Set efficiency flag for L1T online DQM ratio plots to avoid them being normalized in the GUI.
Also fixes some copy and paste errors in the CaloLayer2DEClient.

This is a backport of #20935 but also includes the PRs #20206 and #20583, which are not in 9_2_x yet. The two additional PRs were merged to avoid conflicts when cherry-picking my three commits.
title: L1T online DQM - set efficiency flags - 92x
